text: British International School of Phnom Penh is an international school in Sangkat Prek Eng, Khan Chbar Ampov, Phnom Penh, Cambodia. It was formerly in the Boeung Keng Kang I area of Phnom Penh. It was established in 1995. ==References== ==External links== * British International School of Phnom Penh Category:British international schools Category:International schools in Cambodia
